body:
With this sidemod for the Cobblemon mod, you can fully customize shiny spawn rates for specific Pokémon, giving you control beyond the default settings. Normally, Cobblemon applies a universal shiny rate to all Pokémon, but this mod introduces a flexible configuration system. Now, you can target specific Pokémon and adjust their shiny rates based on Pokémon Properties, similar to how you spawn or edit Pokémon using commands.

For example, to increase the shiny odds of Moltres, you can set a custom config like this:

```JSON
{
  "debug": false,
  "overrides": {
    "moltres": 20.0,
    "ponyta galarian": 100.0
  }
}
```

This setup gives Moltres a 1/20 chance of spawning as a shiny when it spawns naturally in your world, and Galarian Ponyta gets 1/100. Tailor the shiny rates of any Pokémon to create the perfect experience in your Cobblemon adventure!
